#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.dot.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.dot"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:1 of
msgid "Compute the matrix multiplication between the DataFrame and other."
msgstr "计算 DataFrame 与 other 之间的矩阵乘法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:3 of
msgid ""
"This method computes the matrix product between the DataFrame and the "
"values of an other Series, DataFrame or a numpy array."
msgstr ""
"此方法计算 DataFrame 与另一个 Series、DataFrame 或 numpy 数组的值之间的"
"矩阵乘积。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:6 of
msgid "It can also be called using ``self @ other`` in Python >= 3.5."
msgstr "在 Python >= 3.5 中，也可以使用 ``self @ other`` 调用此方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:8 of
msgid "The other object to compute the matrix product with."
msgstr "用于计算矩阵乘积的另一个对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:11 of
msgid ""
"If other is a Series, return the matrix product between self and other as"
" a Series. If other is a DataFrame or a numpy.array, return the matrix "
"product of self and other in a DataFrame of a np.array."
msgstr ""
"如果 other 是一个 Series，则返回 self 与 other 的矩阵乘积作为一个 Series"
"。如果 other 是一个 DataFrame 或 numpy.array，则返回 self 与 other 的矩阵"
"乘积，结果为一个 DataFrame 或 np.array。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.dot`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:19 of
msgid "Similar method for Series."
msgstr "Series 的类似方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:23 of
msgid ""
"The dimensions of DataFrame and other must be compatible in order to "
"compute the matrix multiplication. In addition, the column names of "
"DataFrame and the index of other must contain the same values, as they "
"will be aligned prior to the multiplication."
msgstr ""
"为了计算矩阵乘法，DataFrame 和 other 的维度必须兼容。此外，DataFrame 的"
"列名和 other 的索引必须包含相同的值，因为它们将在乘法之前对齐。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:28 of
msgid ""
"The dot method for Series computes the inner product, instead of the "
"matrix product here."
msgstr "Series 的 dot 方法计算的是内积，而不是这里的矩阵乘积。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:32 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:33 of
msgid "Here we multiply a DataFrame with a Series."
msgstr "这里我们将一个 DataFrame 与一个 Series 相乘。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:44 of
msgid "Here we multiply a DataFrame with another DataFrame."
msgstr "这里我们将一个 DataFrame 与另一个 DataFrame 相乘。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:52 of
msgid "Note that the dot method give the same result as @"
msgstr "注意，dot 方法给出的结果与 @ 相同"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:59 of
msgid "The dot method works also if other is an np.array."
msgstr "如果 other 是一个 np.array，dot 方法也可以工作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic.dot.dot:67 of
msgid "Note how shuffling of the objects does not change the result."
msgstr "注意对象的打乱不会改变结果。"

